310
00:19:13,100 --> 00:19:14,690
Wala kaming pagpipilian noon.

311
00:19:14,980 --> 00:19:16,460
Kailangan nating lahat kumita para sa ating mga pamilya

312
00:19:16,460 --> 00:19:17,790
