Ang iyong munting fangirl, si Wan Qing.

434
00:28:10,110 --> 00:28:11,180
Hindi ba siya lasing?

435
00:28:11,820 --> 00:28:12,450
Oo.

436
00:28:12,770 --> 00:28:15,290
Siya ay nasayang at napilitan si He Zhang

437
00:28:15,290 --> 00:28:16,330
